@milestone First spike - simple pj-task-next, list, done +done
  @iteration @feature task-list - read TODO and print to console +done
    @task Write a new feature +done
    @task Write step definitions +done
    @task Write code to make feature pass +done
      @task @tdd Write Todo.read +done
        Write failing test +done
        Write code to make test pass +done
      @task @tdd Write Todo.to_console +done
        Write failing test +done
        Write code to make test pass +done
      @task @tdd Write Commands::Task::list +done
        Write failing test +done
        Write code to make test pass +done
      @task @tdd Write TodoFile.read_file +done
        Write failing test +done
        Write code to make test pass +done
      @task Write executable script +done
      @task Update specs to explain failing behaviour +done
      @task Update code to pass specs +done
      @exec='cucumber features' Passing features +done
  @iteration task-next - read TODO and print next/current task with context +done
    @task Write a new feature +done
    @task Write step definitions +done
    @task Write code to make feature pass +done
      @task TodoFile should have a tree of items +done
        Create a separate task class +done
        Give task class a parent and children +done
        Give todoFile a list of roots +done
      @task @tdd TodoFile should have a current Task +done
      @task @tdd Commands::Task::Next should output the current task and context to console +done
        Write current_to_console method in TodoFile +done
      @task Write executable script +done
      @exec='cucumber features' Passing features +done
  @iteration @feature task-done - mark a task as done and move the current task pointer +done
    @task Write a new feature +done
    @task Write step definitions +done
    @task Write code to make feature pass +done
      @tdd Todo file should have save behaviour +done
      @tdd Task file should separate description from state +done
      @tdd Task should allow state to be modified +done
      @tdd Commands:Task::Done should load the TODO set the current task to done and save the todo file +done
@patch Add executables to gem +done
  Move script folder to bin folder +done
  Up patchlevel +done
  Release
